snippet.title: Asteroids Do Concern Me - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download it Now!
http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Asteroids-Do-Concern-Me/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258550716

"Out beyond the edge of the universe. Far past any celestial wilderness you could hope to imagine, lies a vast ocean of impenetrable rock...". Test your piloting skills in this addictive one button action game. With 4 different modes ranging from Classic to Double Rainbow. The odds of surviving this game are 3720 to 1. Have you got the minerals? 

Asteroids Do Concern Me is an addictive, one-button, action game.  A fresh and innovative take on the classic "Helicopter Game".

Download it Now!
http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Asteroids-Do-Concern-Me/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258550716

Release Date:  December 7th, 2010
